{"tid":2410826,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"消委會：素漢堡包平均鈉含量比一般牛肉漢堡包高","createTime":"2021-02-17T02:30:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T10:47:03.000Z","uid":278587,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2638242dbbbb09d6d97c13252d6a26c3ece1e94c","tid":2410826,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T02:30:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575997-20210217.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575997-20210217.htm&d=2uuoLuAEMU6cBVSXjgSp%2BZODbC9uMYpCHTvDpi7yeoo%3D&h=64004f13\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575997-20210217.htm&h=da9c8885\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575997-20210217.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n消委會聯同食安中心測試市面10類共99款素菜樣本，發現當中5類，包括素漢堡包、粟米素魚塊、齋鹵味拼盤、素魚香茄子和羅漢齋，鈉含量均高於整體素食樣本的平均值。當中素漢堡包的平均鈉含量最高，比一般牛肉漢堡包可高達2成。測試同時發現，素漢堡包平均飽和脂肪含量是今次樣本中最高。<br />\n<br />\n糖含量方面，以每100克計算，菠蘿素咕嚕肉的平均糖含量最高，當中2款樣本檢出含12克糖，是所有素菜樣本中糖含量最高；其次是齋鹵味拼盤，平均含7.1克糖。<br />\n<br />\n至於總脂肪含量，以每100克計算，芋頭魚及粟米素魚塊樣本的總脂肪含量最高，平均含量分別為17克及13克；素福建炒飯及羅漢齋的平均總脂肪含量則最低。測試又發現，鈉含量最低的1款芋頭魚樣本，反而總脂肪含量是各樣本中最高，檢出每100克含23克總脂肪，達到「高脂肪」食物的水平。<br />\n<br />\n消委會建議市民點餐時可要求「少鹽」，並要求將醬汁分開盛載，經油炸烹調的素菜的總脂肪含量一般較高，應減少進食。"},{"pid":"d4cbcc9236970b4b3d27f4f41307ca2009617069","tid":2410826,"uid":39206,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T10:27:35.000Z","msg":"食素唔洗付出代價呀？"},{"pid":"08af3a1d2c3e5b6303eecaebe1c58e94afdf0282","tid":2410826,"uid":74339,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T10:39:41.000Z","msg":"咁2成都仲係合理範圍 科技再進步應該就會再少啲"},{"pid":"02301b5190444a65da9ddc272bfbe37394c9561a","tid":2410826,"uid":118716,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T10:40:55.000Z","msg":"本身冇味咪係咁加調味囉"},{"pid":"b98fc363fb8488bfaf921525408eaadcbe2a14f6","tid":2410826,"uid":4440,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T10:44:02.000Z","msg":"素肉比起真肉仲唔健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4972cff4baf779a25930fbb395c1c8739763af0","tid":2410826,"uid":61359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T10:44:37.000Z","msg":"仲以為講緊beyond meat"},{"pid":"71db551560e6903b2159ee89951c5513f4f2d12e","tid":2410826,"uid":349058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T10:46:07.000Z","msg":"唔係咁邊有味"},{"pid":"3503989c50f8258297b22b8939a859c6868a9995","tid":2410826,"uid":159870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T10:47:03.000Z","msg":"菜都有生命架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}